    rdfs:comment "SUPERSEDED - KEPT FOR REFERENCE Ontology for AEC drawing elements - facade, structural, and drawing metadata. Based on schema rev02 (06.04.23). Created/edited with https://alelom.github.io/OntoCanvas/ version 0.1.0" ;
